***Winter Abrams***
This is the first vehicle remake from my 1.6 desert vehicles pack and contains a non driveable tank with winter camo.I am still working on interior and trying to make it work and shoot.
Inside the arhive u will find the vmf, and a folder with the custon texture( the folder contains the sesert, forest winter textures) so u can camouflage the tank how u want. I wait assesments, sugestion ideas or just a point a view.
I will try to release the other vehicles to but im still working on the interiors.
<b><font color="red">NOTES: Just copy the camo folder to the materials folder...
Ex: D:\Games\Counterstrike:source\cstrike\materials.
Dont forget to give credits
